<%- include('partials/header') %>
<div class="container">
    <div class="card px-md-5 card-form" style="background: none; margin-top: 100px;">
        <h1 class="display-4 topic">
            Phase II - The Task Phase
        </h1>
        <hr class="my-3">
        <form action="/login" method="post">
            <div class="row">
            <div class="form-group col-md-6">
              <label for="exampleInputEmail1"><span>Email address</span></label>
              <input type="email" name="username" class="form-control" id="exampleInputEmail1" aria-describedby="emailHelp" placeholder="Enter email" required>
              <small id="emailHelp" class="form-text text-muted">We'll never share your email with anyone else.</small>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group col-md-6">
              <label for="exampleInputtext"><span>Password</span></label>
              <input type="password" name="password" class="form-control" placeholder="Enter Your password" required>
              <div class="text-center my-2">
                <a href="/forgot" style="color:#d9534f; font-size: 14px;">
                    Forgot Password?
                  </a>
              </div>
            </div>
       
            <div class="form-group" style="margin:auto;">
                <input type="submit" value="Login" class="button-success">
            </div>
      
            </div>      
          </form>
     </div>
    <div class="jumbotron" style="background: none;">
        <h1 class="display-4 topic">
            Rules
        </h1>
        <hr class="my-3">
     
        <div class="row">
            
            <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                <p style="color: #d9534f;">Technical</p>
                <ul class="list" style="font-size: 14px;">
                    <li>Participants are required to create the Github repository only subsequent to the task assigned.
                    </li>
                    <li>Any repository created prior to the task assigned will lead to direct disqualification of the participant.</li>
                    <li>Plagiarism is strictly prohibited. If any kind-of plagiarized content is found in the submitted work it will lead to immediate disqualification. </li>
                    <li>Applicants are not allowed to fork repositories on GitHub. </li>
                    <li>All the applicants are requested to maintain proper commits and Read me files for their respective tasks.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                <p style="color: #d9534f;">Non - Technical</p>
                <ul class="list" style="font-size: 14px;">
                    <li>All corporate/content-writing applicants are required to type in their answers in a Google document and name the document with their own Name. 
                    </li>
                    <li>The link of the document is to be put in the input box provided.</li>
                    <li>Plagiarism is strictly prohibited. If any kind-of plagiarized content is found in the submitted work it will lead to immediate disqualification. </li>
                    <li>Ensure that the document is public. Access should be given. Any document with a private link will be rejected automatically.
                    </li>
                    <li> All participants applying under graphic designing/ video editing are required to enter their valid task link in the input box and provide access to the same. </li>
                </ul>
               
                  <!-- <p style="font-size: 14px;">Not registered? <a href="/register" style="font-size: 14px;">Register</a></p> -->
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</div>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>